Package: gethr
Type: Package
Title: Access to Ethereum-based Blockchains through Geth Nodes Using the R Language
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vicente", "Garcia Diaz", email = "garciavicente@uniovi.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The gethr package provides full access to the Geth command line interface for running 
    full Ethereum nodes. With gethr it is possible to carry out different tasks such as mine ether, 
    transfer funds, create contacts, explore block history, etc. The package also provides access 
    to all the available APIs. The officially exposed by Ethereum blockchains (eth, shh, web3, net) 
    and some provided directly by Geth (admin, debug, miner, personal, txpool).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
